    <item>
      <title>贝莱德有 13 亿美元薪酬资金来留住新人才</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/blackrock-s-new-deals-task-fink-with-hanging-onto-key-talent</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拉里·芬克在一年内斥资约 250 亿美元，将贝莱德公司打造成基础设施和私人信贷领域的五大巨头之一。现在，他正专注于吸引公司最新的人才留在公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/blackrock-s-new-deals-task-fink-with-hanging-onto-key-talent</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 13:03:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔讲话前，韩元表现优于新兴市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/south-korea-won-rebounds-outperforms-steady-em-currency-index</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈迅速撤销戒严令后，韩元周三反弹，成为新兴市场货币中涨幅最大的货币。交易员们正在等待美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔的讲话，以寻找美国利率走向的线索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/south-korea-won-rebounds-outperforms-steady-em-currency-index</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 10:59:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔讲话前夕，科技股上涨，股市受提振：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大科技公司的股价上涨推动股市上涨，交易员们仔细研究最新的经济数据，等待杰罗姆·鲍威尔的讲话，以寻找美联储下一步行动的线索。美国国债上涨，美元波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 22:24:35 GMT</pubDate>
